{"tid":2322663,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"金希澈睽違3年跳舞了！「SJ九人合體舞台」逼哭E.L.F","createTime":"2020-12-12T13:07:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-13T04:44:35.000Z","uid":16659,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3c349bf9f9d5ac6b8f7e93b95016d62006973a2d","tid":2322663,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:07:12.000Z","msg":"南韓音樂盛典「The Fact Music Awards」（TMA）12日晚間7點在首爾舉行，因應疫情，紅毯和演出皆採取事先錄製的方式。特別的是，從2017年就因舊傷而停止舞台活動的SUPER JUNIOR金希澈，睽違3年將在TMA頒獎典禮，和成員們一起站上舞台。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5330/d5330912.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5330%2Fd5330912.jpg&h=dda6e967&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲「The Fact Music Awards」SUPER JUNIOR舞台。（圖／翻攝自演出畫面）<br />\n<br />\n合體出席頒獎典禮的SUPER JUNIOR，特別演出明年1月發行的專輯《The Renaissance》的新歌《Burn the floor》的初舞台。成員們手持燈光，有如歌劇般營造出神秘的又詭譎的氣氛，到歌曲中段，金希澈出現在舞台中，這也是SUPER JUNIOR久違的9人舞台，讓E.L.F（粉絲名稱）興奮有感動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5330/d5330914.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5330%2Fd5330914.jpg&h=1bc9e0e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲金希澈睽違3年加入SUPER JUNIOR舞台演出。（圖／翻攝自演出畫面）<br />\n<br />\nSUPER JUNIOR也拿下包括「FANN STAR Choice歌手部門」、「FANN STAR最大得票數歌手部門」，以及「2020年度藝人」等獎項，儘管出道15年，依舊是「韓流的帝王」。"},{"pid":"464759dc1bd0c9425578a174bfdac2718de61da2","tid":2322663,"uid":43061,"like":4,"dislike":32,"score":-28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:07:52.000Z","msg":"斷多次腳🙏🏻"},{"pid":"afb631efac85bb678b75ac084df7aba416c8dc83","tid":2322663,"uid":224479,"like":2,"dislike":9,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T13:09:05.000Z","msg":"希澈老師<br />\n屌你老味<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><i